<paragraph id="FA88D613D62E0EA4B5A0D31AAA64F5F9" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
Brazil • 1 ♂, holotype of 
<taxonomicName id="9A7E5AA173C0140DCDA0ECF306319CD0" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Microdon" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Microdon bispina" order="Diptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bispina">
<emphasis id="D77F7766DEDEF77BB80F9658E1AB84C2" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Microdon bispina</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Hull; 
<normalizedToken id="A2419BD2063EC3819104247D8C44D3E4" originalValue="São">Sao</normalizedToken>
Paulo; H.W. Bates leg.; NHMUK. Label 1 (small, round, red-bordered): &quot;Holo- / type&quot;; label 2: &quot;S. / Paulo&quot;; label 3: &quot;Holotype / Microdon / bispina / Hull&quot;. 
<bibRefCitation id="BC1638DAF64BF902C82FF39F9B04B1EC" DOI="https://doi.org/10.1080/00222934308527386" author="Hull, FM" journalOrPublisher="Psyche" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" refId="B12" refString="Hull, FM, 1943. .https://doi.org/10.1080/00222934308527386" url="https://doi.org/10.1080/00222934308527386" year="1943">Hull (1943)</bibRefCitation>
